{"id":244395,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/翻墙-windows7挂vpn让移动设备翻墙/","date":"2012-08-01T08:00:28Z","modified":"2012-08-01T08:00:28Z","title":"翻墙 | Windows7挂VPN让移动设备翻墙","content":"<p>原文：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1.sinaapp.com/?p=150\">http://cui1.sinaapp.com/?p=150</a></p>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<p>本来是在3ds吧发的</p>\n<p>  结果傻逼百度屏蔽了vpn的地址</p>\n<p>对这种傻逼行为做鄙视</p>\n<p><span>注意事项</span>：<br />  这篇文章用于解决不能使用VPN的移动设备<br />【比如3DS的某些视频功能要翻墙，但是3DS不能用VPN】<br />另外路由器不可，只有无线网卡才可以<br />还有，一次只能连接一个设备<br />不能同时连接多个设备</p>\n<p>1.申请VPN<br />首先来搞一个免费VPN<br />  つながるもん，就是他<br />点击这里申请<br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300923201.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730092320\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730092320_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730092320\" width=\"994\" height=\"558\" /></a></p>\n<p>输入Email继续</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300925051.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730092505\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730092505_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730092505\" width=\"955\" height=\"571\" /></a></p>\n<p>确认 无误点送信</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300926141.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730092614\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730092614_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730092614\" width=\"879\" height=\"377\" /></a></p>\n<p>回到邮箱，点击确认连接<br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300929001.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730092900\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730092900_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730092900\" width=\"1003\" height=\"417\" /></a><br />  好，现在申请成功了。记下来账号密码一会要用到</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300930021.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093002\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093002_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093002\" width=\"977\" height=\"550\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.VPN配置</p>\n<p>  右下角网络连接点右键</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>   </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093124.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093124\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093124_thumb.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093124\" width=\"210\" height=\"75\" /></a></p>\n<p>在弹出的窗口上点这个</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300932071.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093207\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093207_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093207\" width=\"464\" height=\"216\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后选择这一项</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300932211.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093221\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093221_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093221\" width=\"632\" height=\"502\" /></a></p>\n<p>然后这一项</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300932321.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093232\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093232_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093232\" width=\"632\" height=\"502\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>输入服务器地址</p>\n<p>  输入「<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://vpn.tsunagarumon.com\">vpn.tsunagarumon.com</a>」「49.212.48.199」「49.212.0.54」</p>\n<p>三者任意一个</p>\n<p>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300934131.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093413\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093413_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093413\" width=\"632\" height=\"502\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  接下来输入密码</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300936311.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093631\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093631_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093631\" width=\"632\" height=\"502\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  下一步，连接</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300937051.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730093705\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730093705_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730093705\" width=\"632\" height=\"502\" /></a></p>\n<p>链接成功</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  3.无线设置<br />接下来讲无线配置</p>\n<p>首先以管理员权限运行CMD</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300943131.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094313\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094313_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094313\" width=\"291\" height=\"206\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>输入<br />netsh wlan show drivers</p>\n<p>   </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300943431.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094343\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094343_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094343\" width=\"681\" height=\"446\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>然后在给出的信息中找“支持的承载网络”<br />如果是“是”，那么进行下一步<br />  如果是“否”，那么检查一下驱动，一般重新安装最新版本的网卡驱动就能解决</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300944071.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094407\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094407_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094407\" width=\"681\" height=\"446\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  好，接下来建立无线网<br />输入<br />netsh wlan set hostednetwork mode=allow ssid=(这里填名字) key=（这里填密码）<br />把密码和名字填到指定位置<br />回车继续</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300946531.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094653\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094653_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094653\" width=\"681\" height=\"446\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  然后弹出提示<br />配置成功</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300947091.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094709\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094709_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094709\" width=\"277\" height=\"78\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>最后敲入<br />netsh wlan start hostednetwork<br />  启动无线网</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300948161.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094816\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094816_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094816\" width=\"382\" height=\"72\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>好了，无线网配置完成<br />需要说明的是，每次关机，休眠都需要重新运行<br />  netsh wlan start hostednetwork<br />这条命令来重新启动无线网</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  4.无线网与VPN连接<br />在刚才新建的VPN上右键，属性</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300949031.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094903\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094903_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094903\" width=\"830\" height=\"306\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>选到共享选项卡<br />在家庭网络连接那一栏选择刚才建立无线承载网络的网络连接名称<br />  （比如我建立的名称叫无线网络连接 2）</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300949351.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094935\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094935_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094935\" width=\"381\" height=\"452\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>可能需要断开连接才会生效<br />那么就断开咯<br />再次连接</p>\n<p>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300949581.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730094958\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730094958_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730094958\" width=\"841\" height=\"491\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>点连接</p>\n<p>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ201207300950181.png\"><img title=\"QQ截图20120730095018\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/QQ20120730095018_thumb1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"QQ截图20120730095018\" width=\"362\" height=\"386\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>好了，现在就可以开移动设备的WIFI搜索热点了<br />移动设备那边什么都不用设置<br />  只需搜索到刚才建立的热点名称，输入设置的密码<br />直接连接就可以了</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  非常苦逼的事情是3DS被母上大人没收了<br />于是我用自己的手机做演示了<br />以下是油土逼界面<br />推荐的节目都是日文</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/9f858fffe8e6.jpg\"><img title=\"未命名\" src=\"http://cui1-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2012/07/thumb2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"未命名\" width=\"484\" height=\"858\" /></a></p>\n</p></div>\n<div>请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\" https://mycdt0.info\"> https://mycdt0.info</a>，穿墙访问《中国数字时代》（当看到“此网站的安全证书有问题”的提示时，请选择“继续浏览此网站(不推荐)”，忽略证书警告并继续访问网站）。《中国数字时代》开通IPv6，欢迎穿墙阅读。翻越防火长城，你可以到达世界上的每一个角落。（Across the Great Fir